;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248);\">Another aspect is that more than 50% of the overall effect of home decoration is determined by full-house customization. If the custom products fall short, the entire renovation project is considered a failure. It is indeed rare to find a custom store that can satisfactorily meet the basic requirements listed above and present a good result in the customer\'s home. The prices of such products are often deterrents for consumers. Additionally, the showroom of a store doesn\'t necessarily reflect the outcome in the customer\'s home. Many showroom designs are created by specialized exhibition teams and are not feasible in a typical customer\'s home. Therefore, it is safe to say that the design of custom products is the core aspect to consider when comparing different custom products.</p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(217, 217, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-back