(15, 10, 2, 'Expressing Interior Design Trends Through Furniture', 'Architecture sets the scene and provides the framework, but interior design and furniture can have a strong influence on the vibe and mood of a space.', 'Expressing Interior Design Trends Through Furniture', 'Architecture sets the scene and provides the framework, but interior design and furniture can have a strong influence on the vibe and mood of a space.', 'Expressing Interior Design Trends Through Furniture', 'images/blog/expressing-interior-design-trends-through-furniture-1694200354.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: initial; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.75em; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(48, 48, 48);\"><a href=\"https://www.flexform.it/en/brand-identity?utm_medium=website&amp;utm_source=archdaily.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: var(--body-links);\">Flexform</a>’s&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flexform.it/en/products?utm_medium=website&amp;utm_source=archdaily.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: var(--body-links);\">2020 Indoor Collection</a>&nbsp;brings fresh momentum to their aesthetic, pieces that tell the story of an informal yet elegant lifestyle. While the designs are timeless, nonetheless certain tre