(4, 2, 'Walk In', 'Modern Walk In Wardrobe', 'walk-in', NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/product/walk-in-1622623991.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<table class=\"table table-bordered\"><tbody><tr><td>carcase<br></td><td>MDF<br></td></tr><tr><td>Door<br><br></td><td>melamine<br></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br></p>', 'A custom bedroom closet is crucial to maintaining tranquility within the most relaxing space in your home. The walk in shape layout affords you more space for minimal cost. white colour can give your bedroom an elegant vibe. Our smashing custom design options — which includes accessories, finishes and lighting — can take your reach-in closet system to a new level of organization of your daily life<br>', 'The wardrobe is crafted fromMDF, which is uniformed in internal structure, moderate in density, and have consistent dimensions<br>', 1, 1, 1, '2021-06-01 02:44:29', '2021-06-02 00:53:11'),
